From 09776eda84d83244e520f6732eedf3f7b754df3d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 18:38:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve Docker build issues

- Add missing i18n dependencies (i18next, react-i18next, i18next-browser-languagedetector)
- Fix TypeScript error in i18n/index.ts (err parameter type)
- Fix redis version conflict with celery (redis>=4.5.2,<5.0.0)
- Remove unused tailwindcss/postcss/autoprefixer dependencies
- Fix TypeScript error in savanaflow offline-db.ts (index name mismatch)
- Add .gitignore to exclude node_modules
